            <scopecontent id="aspace_f55ddc829fc0204104c67ea55fa753a1">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>The papers are comprised of typescript copies of original manuscript writings of Ralph Emerson, valedictorian of the Yale College Class of 1811. Emerson wrote the papers during his years at Yale and they document student academic life at the beginning of the nineteenth century. The collection has been maintained in the order in which it was received and folder titles are the titles of the writings.</p>
            </scopecontent>
